      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   v-key                  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Data stampa solleciti                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-dat-stp-000      thru acc-dat-stp-999        .
           if        w-cnt-acc-ric-sel    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-ric-sel-999.
       acc-ric-sel-200.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
