      *              * Se Exit                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        v-key                =    "EXIT"
                     move  "E"            to   w-cnt-acc-ric-sel
                     go to acc-cod-age-999.
       acc-cod-age-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Valore impostato in campo di destinazione       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      v-num                to   rr-cod-age             .
       acc-cod-age-400.
