      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   w-let-arc-dcc-flg      .
           move      all   "."            to   w-let-arc-dcc-rag      .
           go to     let-arc-dcc-600.
       let-arc-dcc-450.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
